title: Robin Hobb&rsquo;s Royal Assassin T1 (2008) (FitzFoolio) cbr
description:
A COMIC BOOK ADAPTATION OF ROBIN HOBB'S FAMOUS EPONYMOUS NOVEL..Fitz is the illegitimate son of Prince Chivalry, heir to the kingdom of the Six Duchies. While still a child, he is taken to the Farseer's army base and entrusted to the care of the stableman as a bastard offspring of little importance... Until the day King Shrewd notices him and decides to make him his personal assassin. The first album in a new Soleil collection. Cherche Futurs are adapting the greatest novels of Fantasy and Science Fiction in comic book form.
